  "abstract": "The Department of Agricultural Research\r\nServices (DARS) in partnership with the\r\nInternational Crop research Institute for the\r\nSemi-Arid Tropics (ICRISAT), has released\r\nthree improved sorghum varieties; Pilira\r\n3, Pilira 4 and Pilira 5. These new varieties\r\nreplace Pilira 1 and Pilira 2, released in 1993,\r\nand have since been the only improved\r\nsorghum varieties available in Malawi.",
